title: Agronavti
subtitle: Aplication created for farmers
description: Agronavti is a mobile app that allows Georgian farmers to obtain various agricultural information. I worked on this project with a team of developers at Biznetx LLC. I was responsible for the refactoring/improving back-end services and improving coherency of the back-end and client side.

title: Wenu
subtitle: Ordering made simple
description: Wenu is a suit of mobile & web applications that replaces classic paper menus and allows users to book tables, make orders, etc. I worked on this project with a team of developers at Biznetx LLC. I was responsible for the refactoring/improving back-end services and improving coherency of the back-end and client side.

title: Vintage
